Atlanta Hawks Beat Orlando Magic 103-93 in First Round of NBA Playoffs

-- B y   N a n c y   K e r c h e v a l
-- 
2011-04-17T01:51:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-17/atlanta-hawks-beat-orlando-magic-103-93-in-first-round-of-nba-playoffs.html
The  Atlanta Hawks  defeated the
 Orlando  Magic 103-93 in the first round of the National
Basketball Association Eastern Conference playoffs.  The Hawks take a one-game lead in the best-of-seven series
at Amway Center in Orlando,  Florida .  Joe Johson led the Hawks with 25 points followed by  Jamal
Crawford  with 23 points.  Dwight Howard  scored 46 points for the Magic and  Jameer
Nelson  added 27 points.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nancy Kercheval at 
 nkercheval@bloomberg.net  